### ========================================
### MICROSERVICES API TEST FILE
### ========================================
### This file contains comprehensive tests for all microservices
### Tests: Eureka Server, Auth Service, API Gateway, and Monolith
###
### Instructions:
### 1. Start Eureka Server:   cd eureka-server && mvn spring-boot:run
### 2. Start Auth Service:    cd auth-service && mvn spring-boot:run -Dspring-boot.run.arguments="--spring.profiles.active=dev"
### 3. Start API Gateway:     cd api-gateway && mvn spring-boot:run -Dspring-boot.run.arguments="--spring.profiles.active=dev"
### 4. Start Monolith:        cd monolith && mvn spring-boot:run -Dspring-boot.run.arguments="--spring.profiles.active=dev"
### 5. Ensure Redis is running locally (for API Gateway rate limiting)
###
### Variables (set these after getting token):
### @authToken =
### @username = testuser001
### @email = testuser001@example.com
### ========================================

### ========================================
### 1. EUREKA SERVER HEALTH CHECK
### ========================================

GET http://localhost:8761
Accept: application/json

###
