### ========================================
### 7. MONOLITH - QUANTITY ENDPOINTS (Direct, No Auth)
### ========================================

### Get All Quantities (should require auth)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/quantities
Content-Type: application/json

###

### ========================================
### 8. MONOLITH - QUANTITY ENDPOINTS (Via API Gateway)
### ========================================

### Get All Quantities via Gateway (requires token)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/quantities
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer

###

### Create Quantity via Gateway (requires token)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/quantities
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer

{
  "quantityName": "Length",
  "quantityUnit": "Meter"
}

###

### Create Another Quantity via Gateway
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/quantities
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer

{
  "quantityName": "Weight",
  "quantityUnit": "Kilogram"
}

###

### Create Another Quantity
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/quantities
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer

{
  "quantityName": "Temperature",
  "quantityUnit": "Celsius"
}

###

### Get Quantity by ID via Gateway
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/quantities/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer

###

### Update Quantity via Gateway
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/v1/quantities/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer

{
  "quantityName": "Length Updated",
  "quantityUnit": "Centimeter"
}

###

### Delete Quantity via Gateway
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/v1/quantities/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer

###

