### ========================================
### 15. NOTES ON TOKEN USAGE
### ========================================

### After successful login, copy the 'token' value from the response
### Then update the Authorization headers in subsequent requests like:
### Authorization: Bearer <paste-token-here>
###
### Token format in response:
### {
###   "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...",
###   "type": "Bearer",
###   "username": "testuser001",
###   "email": "testuser001@example.com",
###   "userId": 1
### }

